we simply wouldn't be
where we are now without them.

08:40.799 --> 08:45.480
Because these two cars are,
I believe, incredibly important.

08:45.800 --> 08:52.520
It's this pair that took
road cars to and beyond
the 200-mile-an-hour barrier.

08:52.720 --> 08:55.800
Before them we had Countaches
and Testarossas,

08:56.000 --> 09:00.880
